1 A BILL FOR AN ACT relating to agriculture; to amend sections 2-1091,
2 2-1091.02, 2-1095, 2-10,117, 2-2634, 2-3401, 2-4323, 2-4324,
3 49-1499.02, 81-201, 81-2,162.01, 81-2,162.02, 81-2,162.03,
4 81-2,162.04, 81-2,162.05, 81-2,162.06, 81-2,162.07, 81-2,162.11,
5 81-2,162.12, 81-2,162.13, 81-2,162.14, 81-2,162.15, 81-2,162.16,
