8 Reissue Revised Statutes of Nebraska, and section 2-958, Revised
9 Statutes Cumulative Supplement, 2024; to change provisions and fees
10 under the Plant Protection and Plant Pest Act; to provide for the
11 transfer of funds from the Nebraska Potato Development Fund; to
12 change fees under the Pesticide Act; to change powers of the
13 Department of Agriculture relating to the Weeds of the Great Plains
14 book; to provide for the transfer of funds and the elimination of
15 the Weed Book Cash Fund; to terminate the Nebraska Poultry and Egg
16 Resources Act; to change the Nebraska Commercial Fertilizer and Soil
17 Conditioner Act to the Nebraska Commercial Fertilizer and Beneficial
18 Substances Act; to define and redefine terms; to provide for the use
19 of beneficial substances; to change and provide provisions of the
20 Nebraska Commercial Fertilizer and Beneficial Substances Act
21 relating to registration of products, package labeling, fees,
-1-

