1 distribution, and manufacturing; to change the Fertilizers and Soil
2 Conditioners Administrative Fund to the Fertilizers and Beneficial
3 Substances Administrative Fund and change provisions relating to
4 such fund; to eliminate references to soil conditioners; to
5 eliminate provisions relating to certain agricultural associations
6 or societies, certain qualifying organizations, the Nebraska
7 Dairymen's Association, the State Horticultural Society, the
8 Nebraska Livestock Feeders and Breeders Association, the Nebraska
9 Home Economics Association of Organized Agriculture, the Western
10 Nebraska Organized Agriculture Association, the Nebraska Poultry
11 Improvement Association, the Nebraska Potato Council, and certain
12 appropriations authorization; to eliminate obsolete provisions; to
13 harmonize provisions; to repeal the original sections; to outright
