1 assess and collect fees set forth in section 2-1091.02 for inspections,
2 services, or work performed in carrying out subdivisions (8) and (10)
3 through (12) of this section. Inspection time shall be determined based
4 on any portion of a whole hour and shall include the driving to and from
5 the location of the inspection in addition to the time spent conducting
6 the inspection, and the mileage charge shall be for the purpose of
7 inspection. Any fee charged to the department relating to such
8 subdivisions shall be paid by the person requesting the inspection,
