5 director but not exceeding ten cents per ton. The fee shall be set at an
6 amount to cover the expenses of the inspection provided in section 2-4325
7 and the costs of administering this section. The minimum inspection fee
8 required pursuant to this section shall be five dollars, and no
9 inspection fee shall be paid more than once for any one product. In the
10 case of agricultural lime slurry, the fee shall be paid on the base lime
11 material only.
12 (2) If a person fails to report and pay the fee required by
