1 81-2,162.02 For purposes of the Nebraska Commercial Fertilizer and
2 Beneficial Substances Soil Conditioner Act, unless the context otherwise
3 requires:
4 (1) Beneficial substance means any claimed or advertised substance
5 that can be demonstrated by scientific research to be beneficial to soil,
6 media, or at least one species of plant. Beneficial substance:
7 (a) Includes any plant biostimulant, soil amendment, chemical or
